headline: JP Morgan Maintains Neutral Rating on Republic Services (RSG), Lifts PT
summary: On May 23, JP Morgan raised the price target on Republic Services, Inc. (NYSE:RSG) from $229 to $275 and maintained a Neutral rating on the stock. The firm updated the price target after it resumed its coverage of the waste services sector. Republic Services, Inc. (NYSE:RSG) has soared more than 26% on a year-to-date basis […]
